{"word":"ἱπποβάμων","slug":"ἱπποβάμων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἱπποβάμων</b></el> <el>(ἱππο-βά¯μων, ονος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βαίνω'><el>βαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>going on horseback, equestrian</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ρήματα ἱππ.</el> <i>great high-paced</i> words, <i>bombast</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}